
Turntable.fm Bot

Objectives:
 - Prevent idle time from going over x seconds
 - Automatically grab a DJ spot when one becomes available
 - Respond to idle checks

Build:
  coffee --bare -l --watch --compile *.coffee


Possible Additions:
 - If the track is bombing, say something in chat and skip
 - Say something on play to reset idle timers (or right before)
 - Lookup unknown artists on Freebase to determine proximity to a good artist
 	and vote accordingly
 - Turn into a chrome extension, with a button to activate
 - UI improvements

